INSERT INTO `mac_vod` VALUES('12640','渔岛怒潮','','yudaonuchao','Y','','http://i1.letvimg.com/lc02_isvrs/201510/16/11/24/368615e5-58ca-4b6a-a00a-e76e6cb43d5f.jpg','','','温峥嵘,张明健,梁家仁,吕凉,林静,孙桂田,郭凯敏,张颖,吴承骏,','马玉辉,','','正片','大陆','国语','0','12','','','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','504779','0','0','0','0','0','0','9.0','0','230','1480783800','1482347120','0','0','1947年春，胶东解放区龙王岛解放伊始，岛上人员鱼龙混杂，敌我难辨，而我山东战场军火短缺，形势危急。地下党员刘三嫂和中共龙王岛区委书记兼区长叶洪山，接上级胶东军区武装部副部长于德海指示，以办渔业供销社之名，实施“海葵行动”，暗中组织艄公协助军火运输线。恰逢日伪残余势力、海匪渔霸迟龙章计划反攻龙王岛，派出亡命海盗李忠祖“诈死”回岛，组织暗杀排制造恐慌，妄图乱中夺岛。刘叶二人在龙湾头村渔救会长、党支部书记王四江的协助下，粉碎了暗杀排一系列阴谋，更揪出了潜伏极深的特务刘志山。山东战局突变，我军暂时战略转移，龙王岛一度被迟龙章占据，但刘三嫂与我留守军民不屈不饶、坚持敌后斗争，叶洪山则在龙王岛周边继续游击战。在他们的不懈努力下，我军最终顺利完成“海葵行动”，彻底解放龙王岛，打倒了反动派，扭转了战局。','letv$$$sohu','$$$','$$$','http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/23789442.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/23789502.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/23789596.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/23789653.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/23789737.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/23789833.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/23792760.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/23792657.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/23792918.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/23792987.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/23793234.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/23793424.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/23793575.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/23793657.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/23793698.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/23793736.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/23793781.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/23793820.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/23793867.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/23793900.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/23793966.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/23794032.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/23794081.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/23794133.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/23794183.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/23794304.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/23794357.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/23794434.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/23